    <div id="rules-text">
        <ul>
            <li>Objective Crack the Code!<br>
                <bold>Your objective is to use the 6 colors provided with the hints provided at the end of each round to
                    crack the code.</bold><br>
                <small>The Code is automatically generated at the begining of the game. It is revealed at the end of the
                    game.</small>
            </li>
            <li>
                1. Select 4 colors at the bottom of the board.
            </li>
            <li>
                2. Each row represents a round. At the end of each round you will be given hints.<br>
                <small>Hints: White represents - correct position and color. Gray represents - correct color but in the
                    wrong position. Black represents - a color not in the Code.<br>
                    You have 8 rounds to crack the code.</small>
            </li>
            <li>
                3. Use the hints to direct your guess for the next round.
            </li>
            <li>
                4. Good luck! If you are unable to crack the code in 8 rounds; the game resets and you can play again.
                <small>The code will be regenerated, so you will not be cracking the same code.</small>
            </li>
        </ul>
